title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Top 5 busiest airports - France
description:
In this video we will look at the top 5 busiest airports in France. This top 5 contains 3 airports which have been updated by the community so a lot of details can be seen when visiting those airports.

00:00 intro
00:10 Toulouse Blagnac airport(LFBO) 
06:24 Lyon Saint Exupery airport (LFLL)
12:34 Nice Airport (LFMN)
19:14 Paris Orly (LFPO)
21:41 Paris Charles de Gaulle (LFPG)
